Japan's moves for militarist expansion under fire 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, November 9 (KCNA) -- A spokesman for the National Democratic Front of South Korea (NDFSK) issued a statement on Nov. 7 denouncing Japan's daily escalating moves for overseas aggression, according to the Seoul-based radio voice of national salvation.
 Referring to the fact that Japan recently rigged up the "anti-terrorism special law" under the pretext of "assisting the U.S. in its retaliatory war against terrorism" despite strong opposition at home and abroad, the statement said: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 This goes to prove that Japan has entered the stage of realizing the ambition for overseas aggression which it has persistently pursued over the last 50 odd years since its defeat. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The  NDFSK condemns the adoption of this law as a vicious challenge and an unpardonable crime against all Koreans who have demanded Japan make an apology and compensation for its past crimes and opposed its overseas expansion and strongly demands it nullify the law. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Japan is well advised to face up to the trend of the times, properly understand our people's strong will against Japan, drop its design for overseas aggression and make a sincere apology and compensation for its crimes committed against our nation. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The whole nation should foil the Japanese reactionaries' reinvasion through a nation-wide anti-Japanese resistance and force them to pay for their crimes in order to give vent to its grudge. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The NDFSK will join all the people and the world peace-loving people in the anti-Japanese resistance and decisively smash Japan's ambition for reinvasion.

Abolition of S. Korean "Security Law" called for 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, November 9 (KCNA) -- Rodong Sinmun today in a signed article calls for the repeal of the South Korean "Security Law" (SL) which defines the fellow countrymen in the north as the enemy, suppresses and punishes any South Korean desirous of reunification on the charge of being "elements benefiting the enemy" and obstructs the implementation of the June 15 North-South Joint Declaration.
 As long as this law remains in force in South Korea, it is absolutely impossible to achieve national reconciliation and unity nor is it possible to make contacts and exchange between the north and the south successful in conformity with the nation's desire for reunification, the article says, and goes on: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The repeal of the SL is urgently required by the times. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The era of independence and reunification calls upon the Korean nation to reject foreign domination and interference and work for reunifying the country independently and peacefully by its concerted efforts in the spirit of the joint declaration. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The SL has been rebuffed and condemned not only by the Korean nation but the world progressive people and has no justification to remain in force as it is an anti-national, anti-reunification law going against such trend of the times and the nation's desire for independent reunification. The SL is a stumbling block lying in the way of implementing the joint declaration. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It is because of this law that those people in South Korea who long for the north and aspire after the independent reunification are treated as "criminals" and taken to prison. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The South Korean authorities are clamping down upon pro-reunification patriots by invoking the SL and are frantically stepping up arms buildup and war exercises against the fellow countrymen in the north on the strength of this law. This is, in essence, a perfidy to the north, the other party of the dialogue for reunification, and a treachery negating the spirit of the joint declaration. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The SL is a symbol of confrontation with the north and anti-reunification acts. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The South Korean authorities should abolish the ill-famed SL. This is the way for them to shake off the disgrace of being an anti-reunification separatist group and escape from the nation's curse and condemnation. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 They should opt to immediately scrap the anti-national, fascist and anti-reunification SL as demanded by the era and the nation.

New type of lathe manufactured in Korea 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, November 9 (KCNA) -- A new type of digital control electric discharge processing lathe was manufactured by Kim Chaek University of Technology, a seat of scientific and technological education in the DPRK.
 The lathe is based on an organic combination of machine engineering and electronic engineering technologies. It consists of its body, digital control device, power supply device for electric discharge, processing liquid supply device and program making device (32bit). &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 This tool is capable of efficiently cutting all kinds of mouldings and third dimensional parts requiring precision. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Its rate of moulding cutting is ten times that of the existing one. The largest processing length is 450300 200 mm3 and the highest processing speed 250 mm3/min. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 This type of lathes are widely introduced to different industrial establishments and exported to other countries.
